Plugin Changelog
================

1.3

* Add ratelimit for pfctl operations
* Add depend on CARP

1.2

* Add firewall alias support
* Add cache file support for faster recovery after system reboots

1.1

* Add experimental point-to-point device upstream support (e.g. PPPoE)

1.0

* Initial Release
